Fourth Department,

October, 1945.

(October 3, 1945.) Nick Soporito, Respondent, v. Hetzler Foundries, Inc., Appellant.

Orders affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements. All concur. (The orders deny defendant’s motion to dismiss the amended complaint.) Present — Taylor, P. J., Harris, MeCurn, Larkin and Love, JJ. [See post, p. 1010.]
